event.descr:
The appliance is in the process of rebooting. The name of the user who initiated the reboot is contained in amx5020TrapObjectUserName. If the reboot is initated from via snmp , then the value of this object will be the following string snmpUser

amx5020TrapObjectUserName %parm[#1]%;

A connection between a UserStation and an Amiq device has been established. The Uid of the UserStation involved in the connection is contained in amx5020TrapObjectUserStationUid. The Uid of the Amiq device involved in the connection is contained in amx5020TrapObjectAmiqUid. The connection mode of the connection is contained in amx5020TrapObjectAmiqConnectMode
